name: SGS Tapes & Packaging
overview: Established in the year 2010, at Pune (Maharashtra, India), we, ”SGS Tapes & Packaging” are successfully ranked amongst the top manufacturer and supplier of world class array of BOPP Self Adhesive Tapes, Printed BOPP Tapes. The offered products are widely used in industries like foods & beverages, cosmetics & toiletries, agriculture, chemical and pharmaceutical. etc. These are recognized for their durability, smooth finishing and Eco-friendliness. Our product range is safe & easy to assemble and low in maintenance. These products are developed using world class raw material that is procured from some of the trusted vendors of the industry. These are manufactured by our experienced professionals in accordance with international quality standards.
